@node "Description" "Description"


 Description
 ===========

   I decided to make this little utility to simplify use of mpega utility
  of great Stephane Tavenard. Actually this 1.2 version of MPEG
  AUDIO GUI support all the options of mpega 1.1 version (see the
  documentation of mpega).

@endnode

@node "Installation" "Installation"


 Installation
 ============

   To Install MpegA_GUI on your HD simply double-click "Install" icon.
 The installation procedure use the standard "C:Installer" program of
 Commodore Amiga.
@endnode

