@node "System Req." "System Requirements"

 System Requirements
 ===================


 You need  : o  Kickstart 2.04 or above

             o  at least a 68020 CPU

             o  mpega command in your C: directory
                (NOTE: mpega is copyright (c) 1995 by Stephane Tavenard)

             o  GadTools.library in LIBS: directory

             o  XEN.font 8 in FONTS: directory

             o  ASL.library in LIBS: directory
@endnode

