@node "Options" "Options"


 MpegA_GUI Options
 =================

 Descriptions of avaible buttons:

 o INPUT        - Select Mpeg input audio file (.MP2)

 o OUTPUT       - Select Mpeg decoded output audio file

 o Freq Div     - Modify the Freq Div between 1-2-4

 o Quality      - Modify the quality between Worst-Best
                  (Note: Best is avaible in the registered version!)

 o Shift Bit    - Implement the output Shift Bit option

 o i            - See the "about" window

 o PLAY         - Play the current mpeg audio file in standard Amiga
                  8 bit audio mode.

 o DECODE       - Decode input mpeg audio file to output file

 o AIFF option  - Use this option to create an AIFF output file
                  (Note: Avaible only in the registered version!)

 o Mono Output  - This option make a MONO output audio file

 o Audio Filter - If active make audio filter ON! This function have
                  effects only when use PLAY mode.

@endnode

